Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can walk on my own two feet here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I command you in the name\Nof royal Versian blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah, awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only have you survived, you have\Nassumed command of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am most impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am proud of you, Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have grown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been through much. People tend\Nto change as they gain experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the red sands of our home,\NI pray for your success in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You never change at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trident Base, this is Capt. Magbaredge\Nof the Deucalion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Requesting docking clearance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome to Trident, Deucalion.\NYou are cleared to dock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please berth at pier 12.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deucalion, acknowledged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Course, Trident Base docking bay, pier 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the ship with\Nthe Martian tech...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's crewed by children who aren't\Neven old enough for the reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the world coming to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They must have scrounged up every\Nsquad capable of making it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is going to\Nbe a massive operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deceleration complete in 5 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engines, all stop. We are now\Nat a stop relative to pier 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Power down engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once mooring is complete,\Nbegin inspections and resupplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Kaizuka, are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, I guess.\NIt still hurts a little, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better when I take them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it degrades the sensitivity of the neural link.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like an\Nordinary eye to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How well does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get by with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a developmental prototype,\Nso the code needs to be improved,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I can make out most things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weight, 49.2kg.\NHave you gained a little weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used 3D measurements to calculate\Nthe change in momentum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you caught that 200g pack\Nand worked out your total mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I subtracted the estimated weight\Nof your uniform from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting fat! I have more muscle\Nmass from exercising, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie. I can see stress in the\Nformant analysis of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's not broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's working perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see identical stress\Npatterns in her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, Vers Empire Princess Royal\NAsseylum Vers Allusia...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on! If that is a lie, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she isn't really the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This part's waveform is definitely a lie.\NHave you been stress eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been stress eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your stress went up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking to you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. I thought it would\Nbe easy to read Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That clinches it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an idiot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eddelrittuo, shouldn't you\Nbe with Princess Lemrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NI won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. We spotted that\Nship you told us about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Deucalion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they were\Nsecretly repairing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reports say it defeated Baron Yacoym\Nand came up into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might be forced to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose that would make\NPrincess Asseylum sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when she will wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if she never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will see her smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have asked Asseylum\Nto do what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has been arranged.\NYou may rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I once lied to him that she\Nhad been assassinated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now I am lying to him\Nthat she is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine. What is your opinion\Nof Vers as it is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not my place to offer an\Nopinion on our sacred homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is all right.\NYou may speak freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it is possible for our society,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with its powerless,\Nimpoverished citizenry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to become prosperous by conquering Earth,\Nmaking it a domain, and taking its resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That wealth is likely to find its way\Nto only the upper classes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and will not improve the lives\Nof the citizens in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is your suggestion, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who possess Aldnoah\Ncontrol everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the problem in a nutshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well put.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We owe much to His Imperial Majesty\Nfor unearthing Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a grave sin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to hoard that power and create a society\Nwhere the powerful control all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we have achieved victory and seized\Nthe Earth, that red world will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your strength, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my beloved steed ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've finished its activation tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've finished fine-tuning the sync\Nbetween each unit, it will be combat-ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do that on the island!\NStygis Squadron, prepare to move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tharsis, stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not powering up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its Aldnoah Drive is offline...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you deactivated the Tharsis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only one here who can forcibly\Ndeactivate Aldnoah is Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please activate the Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you should ask my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It had always struck me as odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you, a Terran,\Noperate the Tharsis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would be happy to know\Nyou still love her in spite of her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we share a father,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no one pays me any heed simply\Nbecause we have different mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is not true at all.\NWe all admire you, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is. It's not me that you admire,\Nit's my activation factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that exactly why you came to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Aldnoah so important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I my sister's replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was born on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When my scientist father died,\NI lost my one protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I became a servant\Nof the Vers Orbital Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will not say that\NI understand your hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I, too, have known cruel\Ntreatment due to my birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand your suffering,\Nif only some small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do have my heartfelt admiration, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lift your eyes, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, activate it once yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good hunting, Sir Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Milord Slaine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That display was touching.\NI am proud that you are my master.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that? How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All units, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Destination, Marineros Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that was yours,\NI will take on as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So rest easy, dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon enter Earth orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will perform an aerobrake maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,slingshot around,\Nand enter the Satellite Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will then make for\NMarineros Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Slaine, it is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you are aware, the countless rocks\Nthat comprise the Satellite Belt
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,travel in an elliptical orbit\Naround the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trident Base is one of those rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is the orbit of Marineros,\Nthe frontline base of the Mars Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The two will make a close approach\Nin 72 hours' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The distance between them\Nwill be a mere 7km.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's close enough to be\Nseen with the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, a large-scale battle\Nis expected between our two bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operating under that assumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have gathered you here\Nfrom both orbit and the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to assemble a powerful fighting force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is thought that the Mars Army will also\Namass their forces for an all-out offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exercise caution while attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mission is as follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've never fought a space battle\Nof this scale since the war began.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We predict an increase in high-density rocks\Nin the area at the time of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As a result, long-range fire will be\Nthrown off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? But considering that it'll\Nbe a first for the enemy, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your chances of landing a hit will be low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's probably nothing\Nto be scared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But this will hold true for the enemy, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, it is still\Na subject for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Judging from the Mars Army's\Nfighting style to date,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}they have a tendency to put more emphasis\Non offense than defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As such, there is a high probability of them\Nmobilizing their base's mechanized units
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you let that endearing side show\Nevery day, you'd be sure to get a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and engaging us in close-quarter combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deceleration complete in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A little something for the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis Platoon, show me\Nwhat you are made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis 1, by your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis 2, by your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis 3, by your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Intense heat signatures closing\Nin from LEO at high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not reading an IFF signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From below?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They will pass within 2km of this base
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on a trajectory that will take them\Nto the Mars Army's Marineros Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from HQ to intercept, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ships closing in at high speed.\N7 mid-sized ships, and 3 small units.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to launch a surprise attack\Nprior to the all-out offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scramble all operational shipboard Kataphrakts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And prep the ship\Nfor emergency launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is mine ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repairs are complete. It's also fully\Nkitted out with a space loadout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to keep this gaudy\Ncolor? Give the word, and I'll paint it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's supposed\Nto attract attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ghanaati Platoon, in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harroway Platoon, in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 11, in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 22, in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Relative velocity with enemy units\Nis 3kps. They'll pass by in a flash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that their chances\Nof attacking are slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis 1, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis 2, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis 3, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind is complicated. Neither one\Nof us will land a hit at this range.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone's shots landed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this range?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 00, commencing attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compensating for gravity gradient\Nresulting from dense satellite clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Target set...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Stygis Platoon, it's–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you all right, Count?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Slaine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will act as a decoy\Nto draw their fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Harklight, take evasive action.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're going to hit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did it move like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's pinpoint accuracy! How are\Nshots landing in this wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's anticipating the rounds' trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An orange Kataphrakt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I guess you did a class change\Nand are Gull now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy convoy is almost in\Neffective firing range!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy convoy has passed.\NNow breaking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Continue firing until enemy is out\Nof range! Give me a damage report.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tharsis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The personal Kataphrakt of\NOrbital Knight Count Cruhteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Later owned by Count Saazbaum\Nand piloted by a knight under his command.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The orange Kataphrakt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that boy prefers\Nto only pilot trainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho Kaizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard.
